<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tiripuvaṉaccakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>irā<hi rend="grantha">jai</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>tevaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="18"><g type="numeral">10</g> 8</num><g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation"/>vatu kāttikaimātam piṟanta patiṉeḻāṉ tiyati<unclear>y</unclear>āṉa nāyaṟṟukkiḻamaiyum revatiyum <hi rend="grantha">daśa</hi> miyum peṟṟa 
<lb n="2"/>Iṉṟu ceṉṉa(t)tikkāṉaiyāṉa yātavarāyar mutalikaḷil niṉṟaiyil kuḷattuḻāṉ tirukkāḷattiuṭaiyāṉāṉa <unclear>vi</unclear>llavarāyar makaḷār yacciyapāṭiyil kaliccittaṉ tiruvekampamuṭaiyā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rkkup pukka komaḷavalliyeṉ Uṭaiyār tiruvaṇṇāmalaiuṭaiya nāyanā<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>kku vaitta tirununtāviḷakku Oṉṟukku viṭṭa cāvā muvā vāṭu ṉūṟu I<supplied reason="omitted">v</supplied>vāṭu ṉūṟuṉ tiruviḷakkumaṉṟāṭiva
<lb n="4" break="no"/>cam viṭṭuc cantirātittavarai celvatāka viṭṭeṉ komaḷavalliyeṉ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Itu paṉ<hi rend="grantha">mā heśvara rakṣai</hi> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:dash-long" type="punctuation">.</g> piṉpu viṭṭa Āṭu Irupatum Āka Āṭu nūṟṟu Irupatu Ivvāṭu koṭantai ma
<lb n="5" break="no"/>rumakaṉ naṅkaikoṉvacam viṭṭatu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:dash-long" type="punctuation">.</g>
